ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would summarize it as a survey of computational techniques, but mostly focused on data analysis and only a very brief introduction to computational modeling. I would therefore recommend it to a student who wanted exposure to and hands-on experience with data analysis techniques.
Great seminar on different topics in computational neuroscience.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: Did not contribute as of yet. But gave me a great basis to approach different subfields in computational neuroscience.
